You can't go wrong at this brunch spot. Everything we tried was delicious including the French toast and the corned beef hash. The Bloody Mary bar is where it's at though, you get to pick your own assortments. It's also a great view of the Bellagio fountains and Vegas people watching if you can grab a spot outside.

