Pretty solid four stars, the place has a long wait so if you can just sneak up to the bar and eat there. Milkshake was great, fries come with ketchup and some kind of curry --which was a nice touch. The burger itself didn't disappoint, very juicy, great bun and cooked to perfection. It's a lot of food though so come very hungry or just split the burger. I'd definitely recommended this place with no problem, despite the celebrity bits.

